cross: Paphiopedilum Cascading Pink x Paphiopedilum henryanum

measurements.description: One flower and two buds on an 8.5-cm inflorescence, juvenile inflorescence 3 buds; dorsal sepal chartreuse, mahogany spots coalescing into bars; synsepal chartreuse; petals twisted, chartreuse basal one-third transitioning to light brown distal two-thirds, spotted dark brown, hirsute marginally; pouch green overlaid rose-pink; staminode hirsute, green marginally, brown centrally; substance firm; texture matte.
